#: ../../talk/message_integrations.rst:3
msgid "Apps integrating with messages"
msgstr "Aipeanna a chomhtháthú le teachtaireachtaí"

#: ../../talk/message_integrations.rst:8
msgid "Deck"
msgstr "Deic"

#: ../../talk/message_integrations.rst:11
msgid "Create tasks from chat message"
msgstr "Cruthaigh tascanna ó theachtaireacht comhrá"

#: ../../talk/message_integrations.rst:13
msgid ""
"If Deck is installed, you can use the ``...`` menu of a chat message and "
"turn the message into a Deck card."
msgstr ""
"Más rud é go bhfuil an Deic suiteáilte, is féidir leat roghchlár ``...`` "
"teachtaireachta comhrá a úsáid agus an teachtaireacht a thiontú ina cárta "
"Deic."

#: ../../talk/message_integrations.rst:25
msgid "Share card into a chat"
msgstr "Comhroinn cárta i gcomhrá"

#: ../../talk/message_integrations.rst:27
msgid "From within Deck, you can share cards into a chat."
msgstr "Ón Deic, is féidir leat cártaí a roinnt i gcomhrá."
